quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Haa, miim."
  45,2,"Jippagol deftere nde, ko immorde ka Allah, poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo O."
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e tagugol kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin, Ma'andeeji wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  45,4,"Hino e takgol oon ngol kadi, e kon ko O saaki e ruugay…ói, ko Ma'andeeji wonan'de yim…ďe yananaa…ďe …ďeen."
  45,5,"E luutondirgol jehma e √Īalawma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e to…ďo, O wuurnitiri ngo leydi ndin …ďaawo ndi yo'orude, e firlitagol keneeli …óin, ko Ma'andeeji wonan'de yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe …ďen."
  45,6,"∆äiin ko Ma'andeeji Allah …ói Min njanngirante hoore goonga. E ko hol…óum e yewtere …ďe gooŇč…óinta, …ďaawo [yewtere] Allah nden e Aayeeje makko …óeen?"
  45,7,"Bone woodanii kala penoowo bakkodin'…óo !"
  45,8,"Mo no nana Aayeeje Allah …óen hino janngee e dow makko, refti o hedditora e toownitaare, wa si tawii o nanaani …óe. Awa weltinir mo lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  45,9,"Si o anndii go…ó…óum e aayeeje Amen …óeen, o jogitora …óum jalnori. ∆Āeen …óoon, hino woodani lepte koynooje:"
  45,10,"Jahannama hino caggal ma…ď…ďe. Ko …ďe paggitinoo duncanoytaa…ďe hay hu'unde, wonaa kon ko …ďe jogitinoo yi…ó…ďe ko wonaa Allah. Hino woodani …ďe lepte maw…óe."
  45,11,"Ndee [deftere]ko peewal. ∆Āeen yeddu…ďe noon aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen, hino woodani lepte co…ď…óe mu'usuu…óe."
  45,12,"Ko Alla oon woni ko eeltanta mon maaya ngam laa…óe ndoga e hengo e dow yamiroore makko, ngam …óa…ď…ďon e …ďural makko e yaama joo njetton."
  45,13,"O eeltani on ko woni e kammuuji e ka leydi fof, wonii e …óuum kaawisaaji wonan'de yim…ďe miijatoo…ďe."
  45,14,"Maakan …ďeen goon…óin…ďe yoo…ďe njaafa …ďeen …ďe tijjaaki nyal…ói Alla ngam O yo…ďa …ďe yim…ďe ko…ďe paggittono ko."
  45,15,"Kalo gollu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īi,ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnu…óo, yantat e makko refti ko ka Joomi maa woni ruttorde mon."
  45,16,"Min tottii banii Israa*iil deftere e √Īee√Īal e annabaagal Min nje…ói…ďe e dagii…ói Min …ďurni…ďe ko heewi e binnde he."
  45,17,"Min totti dallillaaji …ďannginooji …ďe luuraani si wonah caggal nde ganndal ari e mum en sabu bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe pellet Jooma na √Īaawa hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īande darnga ko…ďe njeddandiratnoo ko."
  45,18,"Refti min mba…óma e laawol e yamiroore amen, woto rew belaa…óe …ďeen …ďe ngannda."
  45,19,"Pellet …ďeen …ďe nafataama gaa e Alla hay hu'unde pellet too√Īoo…ďe yogo e mum en ko weldii…ďe, Alla woni keeda hul…ďe …ďe."
  45,20,"O quraana kombo gite e peewal e yurmeende wonan'de yananaa…ďe …ďe."
  45,21,"Mbele …ďeen wa…ó…ďe boneeji na nanndi e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle lobbe ho…ďe fota e nguurndam mum en e maayde ma…ď…ďe bonii ko…ďe √Īaawata."
  45,22,"Alla tagrii kammuuji e leydi goonga ngam kala fittaandu yo…ďee kondu fagginoo ko kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake."
  45,23,"Mbele a yiaani oon jaggir…óo belaa…óe makko dewetee…óo Alla majjini mbo e dow ganndal O uddi nan…óe makko e …ďernde makko, o wa…ói e gite makko hee cuddi ko hombo feewnata oon caggal Alla mate on miictaaka."
  45,24,"He'efer…ďe mbii …óum wona si wona nguurndam aduna min maaya min nguura, halkataa min si wona jamaanu, …ďe ngalana …óuum ganndal …ďe cikkita tan."
  45,25,"Si aayeeje amen …ďanngu…óe njanngaama e mum en hujja ma…ď…ďe wonata si wona ngaddee baabiraa…ďe amen si on ngonii gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  45,26,"Maaku ko alla wuurnata on refti o wara on refti renndina on fa'ade √Īalawma darnga mbo sikke alah e mum, kono ko …ďuri heewde e yim…ďe ngannda."
  45,27,"Woodanii Alla laamu kammuuji e leydi, √Īande darnga darii √Īande heen meerentee…ďe …ďe perta."
  45,28,"Ha…óa yiya -aan nulaa…óa- kala le√Īol na gurfanii e koppi mum,kala le√Īol na noddiree deftere mum hannde woni ko njo…ďete…óon ko ngollatna…óon e ndeer aduna."
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere amen honde wowla goonga, min ngoniina min ceeraani won'de emin njamira nde winndate ko ngollatna …óon."
  45,30,"Tawi ko …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle lobbe O naatnat…ďe e yurmeende makko, ko …óuum woni mala …ďanngungal."
  45,31,"Tawi ko …ďeen he'efaree…ďe mbele aayeeje am …óe njanngetanooke e dow mon mawnikini…óon laati…óon yim…ďe bon…ďe."
  45,32,"Si …ďe mbiaama pellet fodoore Alla ko goonga sikke alah heen mbi'on min ngannda ko woni darnga, min cikkiti cikkitagol min ngonaani yananaa…ďe."
  45,33,"boneeji …ói …ďe paggitinoo …óiin fe√Īana …ďe, ko …ďe njalkitatnoo kon fiiltoo …ďe."
  45,34,"…ďe mbi'ana hannde min njejjita mon hono no njejjitir…óon pottal √Īangu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni ho…óorde mon on nda√Īata walladii…ďe."
  45,35,"…óuum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla …óe njalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde …ďe njaltata e yiite …ďe nduttataaka aduna …ďe ngolla golle lobbe haa Alla welee…ďe."
  45,36,"Woodanii Alla jettooje nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde."
  45,37,"Na woodani mbo manngu ndeer kammuuji e leydi ko KaŇčko woni mbo gooto foolata √Īee√Ī…óo."
